snippet.textDisplay:
Alright I've read some theories and I've been on a music video binge and I'm definitely getting more of this now.
.
For example, someone pointed out the croquet set at 8:34 as being a reference to the opening of the video for "I'm Not Okay" when Ray is listing all the things Gerard likes, croquet being one of them.
I also find it interesting that some of the people in the comments on that video heard that as cocaine instead of croquet, and a bit before the croquet set shows up, at 8:18, the line "drugs give me drugs" from Na Na Na Na is playing on the car's radio, and I wonder if putting those things together was an intentional poke at that misheard quote, but that may be reaching.
.
I also saw on Wikipedia that MCR used black hooded figures to announce a Black Parade concert in London, much like the figures in this video.
.
Anyways, mysterious MCR video analysis is fun :)
